name: Takeshi's Long Oranges
description:
Originally created in 1998, it was believed that the idea to create Long Oranges started after Takeshi ate an egg mayo sandwich that has lived in his fridge for 37 days. The details were blurry, but he was sure that an old wise camel came by and asked him; "Why eat two oranges when you can eat one long orange?".

2461 x 1969 px
